90
00:07:16,139 --> 00:07:17,740
You can't sleep? Just go and...

91
00:07:20,110 --> 00:07:21,550
Go and get some air by the sea.

92
00:07:23,850 --> 00:07:24,620
Lu Sen.

93
00:07:24,980 --> 00:07:26,620
Why aren't you in bed as well?

94
00:07:27,790 --> 00:07:29,189
I'm just taking a walk.

95
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:32,259
Is this your first time in Xiwan Bay?

96
00:07:32,459 --> 00:07:35,529
The night view here is beautiful.

97
00:07:36,259 --> 00:07:38,560
Ask Shan Shan to take you to the beach.

98
00:07:39,100 --> 00:07:39,899
Grandma.

99
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:41,569
