100
00:07:42,769 --> 00:07:44,699
You look bright-eyed and alert.

101
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:47,310
Lu Sen is my VIP guest.

102
00:07:47,569 --> 00:07:49,339
You have to take care of him.

103
00:07:49,470 --> 00:07:50,810
Since when did he become a VIP?

104
00:07:50,879 --> 00:07:52,480
I just decided that now.

105
00:07:53,180 --> 00:07:55,050
Whoever is handsome...

106
00:07:55,149 --> 00:07:56,680
is a VIP guest to me.

107
00:07:57,850 --> 00:07:58,579
Go on.

108
00:08:05,060 --> 00:08:06,860
Is that your grandma's house?

109
00:08:07,660 --> 00:08:08,860
This isn't my grandma's house.

110
00:08:09,029 --> 00:08:10,529
It's my friend's grandma.

111
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:11,560
