112
00:08:15,199 --> 00:08:16,300
That's amazing.

113
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:17,540
What's amazing?

114
00:08:19,370 --> 00:08:20,709
I've never thought...

115
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:22,769
