121
00:08:35,220 --> 00:08:36,789
No, I'm turning 27 soon.

122
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:38,059
What about you?

123
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:39,320
We're about the same age.

124
00:08:43,389 --> 00:08:45,230
Can I be your friend?

125
00:08:45,399 --> 00:08:46,399
No.

126
00:08:47,100 --> 00:08:48,570
- Why? - No reason.

127
00:08:51,100 --> 00:08:52,399
I think it's going to rain.

128
00:08:55,039 --> 00:08:56,039
I love the rain.

129
00:08:58,139 --> 00:08:59,440
It was also raining that day.

130
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:01,649
And there were fireworks in the sky.

131
00:09:04,019 --> 00:09:05,379
She was standing right in front of me.

132
00:09:06,620 --> 00:09:07,490
Then all of a sudden...

133
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:13,389
Can I tell you...

134
00:09:13,690 --> 00:09:15,259
about the story between me and Friday?

135
00:09:17,129 --> 00:09:19,460
If you're not in a really bad mood,

136
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:22,070
I want to tell you my story.

137
00:09:23,429 --> 00:09:24,669
I don't know why,

138
00:09:25,139 --> 00:09:26,870
but you're the only one that I wish to tell it to.

139
00:09:36,049 --> 00:09:36,809
Go ahead.

140
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:48,230
From the first day she was sent to my house,

141
00:09:49,559 --> 00:09:51,360
I knew she was special.

142
00:10:09,679 --> 00:10:10,850
But in the end,

143
00:10:12,250 --> 00:10:14,019
I made a foolish decision.

144
00:10:14,419 --> 00:10:15,720
I reset her.

145
00:10:17,049 --> 00:10:17,990
It all...

146
00:10:18,789 --> 00:10:19,759
came to an end.

147
00:10:22,090 --> 00:10:23,090
What happened next?

148
00:10:23,730 --> 00:10:25,129
Are you cured?

149
00:10:25,559 --> 00:10:26,659
Are you still alone?

150
00:10:26,730 --> 00:10:27,529
You didn't say any of that.

151
00:10:27,600 --> 00:10:29,029
You can't just tell half of the story.

152
00:10:30,970 --> 00:10:32,240
None of that matters.

153
00:10:32,740 --> 00:10:33,669
Nothing matters.

154
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:34,970
But I want to know.

155
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:40,480
I'm cured and I've made friends.

156
00:10:44,779 --> 00:10:45,879
But it still hurts...

157
00:10:46,919 --> 00:10:48,549
