195
00:12:51,779 --> 00:12:53,080
I commanded her to do deep learning.

196
00:12:53,139 --> 00:12:54,179
I kept inputting data.

197
00:12:55,149 --> 00:12:56,080
But...

198
00:12:57,480 --> 00:12:59,820
