211
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:32,320
My family?

212
00:13:32,519 --> 00:13:35,250
My mom's brother and his wife...

213
00:13:35,320 --> 00:13:36,919
and my younger sister, En Bao.

214
00:13:39,090 --> 00:13:42,490
Then you must be staying at your uncle's.

215
00:13:43,690 --> 00:13:44,759
If you're here,

216
00:13:45,730 --> 00:13:47,870
