217
00:13:49,399 --> 00:13:50,500
Next question.

218
00:13:53,139 --> 00:13:56,769
Who do you want to see the most right now?

219
00:14:01,279 --> 00:14:02,480
I miss my dad the most.

220
00:14:03,409 --> 00:14:04,480
But he...

221
00:14:05,279 --> 00:14:06,879
My dad passed away.

222
00:14:07,889 --> 00:14:09,389
I remember when I was a kid,

223
00:14:10,250 --> 00:14:14,559
he was a mechanic at a garage.

224
00:14:15,730 --> 00:14:17,700
I felt as if he could...

225
00:14:18,059 --> 00:14:20,460
fix any car no matter how broken they were.

226
00:14:21,470 --> 00:14:22,700
I was so envious of him.

227
00:14:22,899 --> 00:14:24,269
I wanted to be like him,

228
00:14:24,340 --> 00:14:26,200
someone who can do what they do best.

229
00:14:26,769 --> 00:14:29,240
So are you doing it now?

230
00:14:30,870 --> 00:14:31,779
I...

231
00:14:32,840 --> 00:14:33,679
You know what?

232
00:14:34,179 --> 00:14:36,279
There's a gap between ideal and reality.

233
00:14:36,580 --> 00:14:39,080
Sometimes, your talent and luck...

234
00:14:39,919 --> 00:14:41,590
aren't good enough for your dream.

235
00:14:42,120 --> 00:14:43,720
Since ages ago,

236
00:14:44,759 --> 00:14:46,090
I've thought of myself as a useless person.

237
00:14:47,159 --> 00:14:48,960
But I had this friend.

238
00:14:49,889 --> 00:14:51,460
He always tells me...

239
00:14:52,500 --> 00:14:53,899
that I am really competent.

240
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:55,269
He even trusts me.

241
00:14:55,730 --> 00:14:57,600
He told me to hold on to my dream.

242
00:15:00,200 --> 00:15:01,639
If your friend knows...

243
00:15:02,039 --> 00:15:04,110
that he means so much to you,

244
00:15:05,139 --> 00:15:06,539
he'll be very happy.

245
00:15:09,450 --> 00:15:10,149
Is that so?

246
00:15:12,279 --> 00:15:13,679
When a person knows...

247
00:15:14,919 --> 00:15:16,990
that he means so much to someone,

248
00:15:17,820 --> 00:15:19,620
he should be very proud of it.

249
00:15:23,289 --> 00:15:23,960
Sure.

250
00:15:24,259 --> 00:15:25,200
Then...

251
