00:33:45,289 --> 00:33:46,759
his condition worsens.

504
00:33:49,299 --> 00:33:50,130
I can't even imagine...

505
00:33:51,299 --> 00:33:53,839
how he'll react if he sees you...

506
00:33:54,400 --> 00:33:55,339
when he wakes up.

507
00:34:06,250 --> 00:34:07,019
Dr. Ou.

508
00:34:07,849 --> 00:34:10,250
Is he out of danger now?

509
00:34:13,920 --> 00:34:14,719
He's alive.

510
00:34:16,860 --> 00:34:18,659
But his connection to the world...

511
00:34:20,860 --> 00:34:22,199
has been ruined by you.

512
00:34:27,099 --> 00:34:27,840
Then he...

513
00:34:28,570 --> 00:34:30,340
Can he be as he once was?

514
00:34:30,840 --> 00:34:32,909
It took me nearly 15 years...

515
00:34:33,639 --> 00:34:35,309
to get him to how he used to be.

516
00:34:35,380 --> 00:34:36,409
Do you think that's possible?

517
00:34:40,449 --> 00:34:41,480
I'm begging you.

518
00:34:41,849 --> 00:34:43,219
If you have any conscience,

519
00:34:43,849 --> 00:34:45,349
stay away from Lu Sen.

520
00:34:46,320 --> 00:34:48,059
The last person he wants to see right now...

521
00:34:48,860 --> 00:34:49,730
is you.

522
00:34:59,500 --> 00:35:01,900
Dr. Ou, I'm sorry.

523
00:35:02,769 --> 00:35:04,809
Please take good care of Lu Sen.

524
00:35:09,210 --> 00:35:10,949
Can you hand this over to him?

525
00:35:14,280 --> 00:35:15,519
I'll make up for all the harm I've caused him...

526
00:35:16,619 --> 00:35:17,750
in due course.

527
00:35:43,849 --> 00:35:44,550
Shan Shan.

528
00:36:10,570 --> 00:36:15,239
(Fu Yang)

529
00:36:15,510 --> 00:36:19,880
(Li Cha De)

530
00:36:19,980 --> 00:36:20,980
(Da Yun)

531
00:36:23,289 --> 00:36:25,050
These are the gifts that Lu Sen got us...

532
00:36:26,820 --> 00:36:27,820
before he got sick.

533
00:36:29,889 --> 00:36:31,289
Lu Sen is so kind to us.

534
00:36:31,590 --> 00:36:33,260
We don't deserve his gifts.

535
00:36:34,530 --> 00:36:35,730
I don't even deserve to think about it.

536
00:36:37,000 --> 00:36:38,969
I wonder if Lu Sen has even eaten.

537
00:36:39,340 --> 00:36:41,000
It's such a big and cold house.

538
00:36:41,940 --> 00:36:43,139
He's so sick,

539
00:36:44,940 --> 00:36:46,579
but there's no one to care for him.

540
00:36:50,750 --> 00:36:52,010
Someone can.

541
00:37:01,289 --> 00:37:04,559
Friday belongs to Lu Sen.

542
00:37:06,329 --> 00:37:07,500
We should return it to its rightful owner.